  "description": "Adjust Image Styling in Embedded Gallery Item Component\n\nUpdate the CSS styling for images within the embedded-gallery-item component to align with the gallery layout design.\n\nRequirements:\n- Set margin-top to 0 for img elements inside embedded-gallery-item\n- Set border-bottom-left-radius to 0 for img elements inside embedded-gallery-item\n- Set border-bottom-right-radius to 0 for img elements inside embedded-gallery-item\n- Verify changes apply correctly to all gallery item states (loading, error, loaded)\n- Test that images align properly with their container borders\n- Ensure changes don't affect images in other gallery components",
